						<summary>

						<p>States that a certain <hi rend="bold">Nārāyaṇa,</hi> son of <hi rend="italic">Daṇḍanāyaka</hi> <hi rend="bold">Vēma-Nāyaka</hi> gave 55 sheep for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mūlasthāna-Mahādēva of <hi rend="bold">Nādiṇḍla.</hi> The first 18 lines are in Telugu verse but the versification is faulty.</p>						

